sub_title: Multi cultiral background, Korean speaking French, English and initiated in Dutch. Enthuasitic in health&food industry. Experienced in managing international client relation, operational streamlining and multi-projects.
summary: An enthusiastic trilingual (English, French and Korean) individual who loves to be in a multi-cultural environment and has earned a degree in Intercultural Project Management and Communication. Currently job searching. Previously, I have worked in a logistic company, I handled responsibilities related to export and import operations. During my studies, I accomplished the internship in the Grand Palais, in mediation-education departement. The taks were mostly to assist organizations of art activities for various public. In addition to this, I also work as a part time translator for different organizations' multicultural programs (main languages being English, French and Korean). All the above experiences hasn made very open-minded and helped me sharpen my social intelligence in a multi-cultural setup. Insta page @ss_ue_luv
